{"tid":2339382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台陸委會證實　向華強向佐已提依親赴台居留申請","createTime":"2020-12-24T14:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T16:58:39.000Z","uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3960b70dd2e78f44fc28511650cc3ef169baa41b","tid":2339382,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"台灣傳媒早前報道，香港著名電影監製向華強近期向台內政部移民署申請赴台依親居留。陸委會發言人邱垂正周四（24日）證實，向華強已提出依親居留申請，目前正由主管機關作業中，但會依法規予以審核。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會周四舉行例行記者會，邱垂正稱，向華強及兒子向佐今年9月初以商務履約名義申請入境，可在台停留3個月，必要時可再延長3個月。據了解，兩人是在台灣停留期間，向移民署提出依親居留申請。<br />\n<br />\n被問及向佐有中共共青團旗下「中華全國青年聯合會」委員的身分，是否違反居留定居等相關規定時，邱垂正表示，政府已修正《香港澳門居民進入台灣地區及居留定居許可辦法》，若有曾任中共黨政軍職的背景，就會經過聯審會。至於向華強、向佐日前提出商務履約需求時，政府也秉持這個精神加以審視，才同意他們赴台進行商務履約。<br />\n<br />\n據報，向華強曾公開支持修定《港區國安法》，妻子陳嵐曾在香港「反送中」期間發表譴責香港青年的文章，有在台港青團體認為不應讓支持中共的港人赴台。邱垂正回應稱，政府都注意到社會對此案的關心，但陸委會尊重主管機關及相關機關，依權責審查這個案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/566184/%E5%8F%B0%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6-%E5%90%91%E8%8F%AF%E5%BC%B7%E5%90%91%E4%BD%90%E5%B7%B2%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9D%E8%A6%AA%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%85%E7%95%99%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;fbclid=IwAR22H_xtPlrdGmcewweopUznHyy9Gdj8d7rv4V71kmdKXzlhIY60JEavgI8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F566184%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25AF%25A6-%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25BD%2590%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25B1%2585%25E7%2595%2599%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost%26utm_campaign%3Dnews%26fbclid%3DIwAR22H_xtPlrdGmcewweopUznHyy9Gdj8d7rv4V71kmdKXzlhIY60JEavgI8&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=e60fc616\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/566184/%E5%8F%B0%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6-%E5%90%91%E8%8F%AF%E5%BC%B7%E5%90%91%E4%BD%90%E5%B7%B2%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9D%E8%A6%AA%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%85%E7%95%99%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;fbclid=IwAR22H_xtPlrdGmcewweopUznHyy9Gdj8d7rv4V71kmdKXzlhIY60JEavgI8</a>"},{"pid":"a89f4affff9ae63cc540827c9cb2d0daf035cb23","tid":2339382,"uid":49776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6b41087c9132a3053bc498225a9c3472ddb840","tid":2339382,"uid":70771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"咁愛國就番大灣區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31620d4cdf53ef5e00c1c2d05d5f67c2e680bb3c","tid":2339382,"uid":235015,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"咁都批既話，不如叫埋習總去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b8428896d21c491c681bb43739e073be13ad2c","tid":2339382,"uid":167931,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"667ee596c4373c53295294e7dd2da42d9ce0732f","tid":2339382,"uid":218166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"唔係咁撚樣都批掛?"},{"pid":"8aba35bb816f2c5edc1444f5ac1127ee2935ae6c","tid":2339382,"uid":35420,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"如果咁都批<br />\n所謂制裁真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話公務員冇得移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\